#: addons/16_Kingdoms___Sea.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10 standard
msgid "16 Kingdoms + Sea"
msgstr "16 royaumes + mer"

#: addons/16_Kingdoms___Sea.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"16 Kingdoms randomly spawned in a new World, nobody ever has seen before. "
"The World is rich, ultra rich. The Kingdoms lifed happy side by side over "
"decades. With all this wealth, they became powerful. But power comes with "
"greed, screaming for more power. This led to a constant arms race.  It was "
"only a matter of time until the first conflicts arose...  Will you keep up "
"against your enemies? Once they start their military power increasing they "
"wont stop until you stop them.  It is recomendet to play this map everyone "
"against everyone, with no diplomacy allowed to become an global "
"autocracy.    Edited: added Harbours, smoothed shorelines, fixed "
"hillsheights so mines should be buildable now everywhere. River has been "
"widened"
msgstr ""

#: addons/16_Kingdoms___Sea.wad/dirnames:4 input:4 standard
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Cartes complémentaires"

#: input:7 input:11 standard
msgid ""
"After this is a HUGE map, you wont see any enemy soon. It took me a while "
"(above 12h) so please leave me a like if you like this map.  Vulcans are "
"rich of gold and coal. But you will find gold and stone everywhere. While "
"coal and iron is the most comon."
msgstr ""
"Bien que ce soit une ÉNORME carte, vous ne verrez pas d’ennemi bientôt. Cela "
"m’a pris un certain temps (plus de 12h) alors s’il vous plaît laissez-moi un "
"like si vous aimez cette carte. Les Vulcains sont riches en or et en "
"charbon. Mais vous trouverez de l’or et de la pierre partout. Tandis que le "
"charbon et le fer sont les plus communs."
